_sText:
A small action-packed fy map with buyzone and many explosives and many things to explore!!
I already played it and it was so funny :D

I tried to create a bit of the 1.5-funmap-atmosphere, and for me it worked  :-)

Btw: There are several "secrets" and hidden paths, good luck finding them :)
Just 1 tip: Climb on the tree to reach the button exploding the big crate in the middle :D
